songs.lyrics:
[Spoken]
I mean a lot of creatives have a lot of emotional stress
Yeah
And that's where a lot of good things come out of, so I think that's one of the reasons why Andy's so great at a lot of the things he does. And I also think that's caused him to be very independent, which is- which is great. Like he's sitting here with a green hat and orange pants, and like a wrestling shirt on
Love it
And I don't know anybody else that would like out like that, but that's exactly what I like about him 'cause he's like, "what? This is is it."
